Rock-Paper-Scissors Web App - Streamlit :

Project Overview
This is an interactive Rock-Paper-Scissors game built using Python Streamlit. Users can:
- Select Rock, Paper, or Scissors
- Play against a computer making random moves
- View instant game results
- Track their score against the computer
- Reset the game anytime

Features
-  Random computer selection
-  Immediate result display
-  Live score tracking (User vs Computer)
-  Reset option to clear scores
-  Clean, responsive UI with emojis

Tech Stack
- Python 3
- Streamlit for frontend/web app
- Random module for computer choices
